{"tid":434523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門今晚掛一號波 周日潮水恐高於路面","createTime":"2017-10-13T11:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T12:43:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d61bc04e0d167222e2a716dc5442f05e4a1445d2","tid":434523,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"澳門地球物理暨氣象局下午2時發出特別報告，指南海的熱帶風暴「卡努」會在今日黃昏前後，進入澳門800公里範圍內，屆時氣象局將會懸掛一號風球。惟局方傍晚改稱，今日晚間才會掛一號波。<br />\n<br />\n按照氣象局最新預測，卡努會以偏西方向移動，橫過南海並繼續增強。在卡努與冬季季候風的共同影響下，廣東沿岸的風力會明顯增強；預計卡努周日早上，會在澳門西南偏南約400公里附近掠過，由於正值天文潮，潮水很可能高於內港路面，呼籲市民提高警惕，提前做好準備"},{"pid":"be9b4d02fab84b4c391cd1fe4a7de8ba4b50c58c","tid":434523,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"再嚟過 加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad0aef72bb0a63b3080255214d2a8728094a479","tid":434523,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e9a16076301789a870bf7e525f7f227777d2ec","tid":434523,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"受死啦澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d2f74f88a34bb5436c9a72faeec31d57415228","tid":434523,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受死啦澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有好多自己友係度，積下口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce90ce89bc9f30273772f44a992705c7cfc59fab","tid":434523,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"吹去海南島都8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /